des:
If you have any problem when you use this skill, you can contact us with email :info@magnumheatinggroup.com
Amazon Alexa and the Magnum MRC Smart WiFi Thermostat work together to help you control home appliance nice and easy.
You can simply ask Alexa to set and query the temperature of Thermostat. 
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust you thermostat - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap or Echo Show. 
After connecting Alexa to your MAGNUM Smart products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "MAGNUM Heat" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one account in the "MAGNUM Heat" app;
(3). You need to have at least one MAGNUM MRC Smart WiFi Thermostat in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "MAGNUM Heat" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in “MAGNUM MRC” skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "MAGNUM MRC" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "MAGNUM MRC”, and you'll be navigated to Magnum login page;
(9). Input your MAGNUM Heat account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished. 
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, What is the temperature of the thermostat?"
“Alexa, Set the thermostat to 20 degrees."
